mxTextCell.title: Text
mxTextCell.label: Hay day - Crops planted up to level 15

mxTextCell.title: Text
mxTextCell.label: In every field the players can cultivate maximum one crop in the same time

mxTextCell.title: Text
mxTextCell.label: Crops are plants players can cultivate on farm land

mxTextCell.title: Text
mxTextCell.label: Players cultivate field crops by planting previously harvested crops into fields. One planted crop gives two harvested ones.

mxTextCell.title: Text
mxTextCell.label:
Specific levels give crops as a reward to players :

- At level 1 they earn "Wheat"
- At level 2 they earn "Corn"
- At level 5 they earn "Soybean"
- At level 7 they earn "Sugarcane"
- At level 9 they earn "Carrot"
- At level 13 they earn "Indigo"
- At level 15 they earn "Pumpkins"

mxTextCell.title: Text
mxTextCell.label:
Every crops have a cool-down to grow and gives xp after harvesting:

- Wheat (2 minutes|1 xp after harvesting)
- Corn (5 minutes|1 xp after harvesting)
- Soybean (20 minutes|2 xp after harvesting)
- Sugarcane (30 minutes|3 xp after harvesting)
- Carrot (10 minutes|2 xp after harvesting)
- Indigo (2 hours|5 xp after harvesting)
- Pumpkins (3 hours|6 xp after harvesting)

mxTextCell.title: Text
mxTextCell.label:
In order to level up, the player needs to earn a specific amount of xp :

- 27 xp to level up from level 1 to level 2
- 7 xp to level up from level 2 to level 3
- 14 xp to level up from level 3 to level 4
- 30 xp to level up from level 4 to level 5
- 50 xp to level up from level 5 to level 6
- 220 xp to level up from level 6 to level 7
- 370 xp to level up from level 7 to level 8
- 490 xp to level up from level 8 to level 9
- 790 xp to level up from level 9 to level 10 
- 960 xp to level up from level 10 to level 11
- 1180 xp to level up from level 11 to level 12
- 1550 xp to level up from level 12 to level 13
- 1790 xp to level up from level 13 to level 14
- 2270 xp to level up from level 14 to level 15
